node.text: This Saturday me & @josievf are coming together to do a full moon circle. This full moon circle will be an opportunity to celebrate the full moon as well as learn both spiritual & self care rituals/methods (based in ritual & plant medicine) for anyone- though it is tailored to support mamas & parents especially. There is a chance to win both a heart activation oil & grounding bath! Entry to the raffle is included with your ticket.
